{"tid":1215962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國駐英大使稱中央從未指示香港修訂《逃犯條例》","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:41:05.000Z","uid":123985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b33a999f6fa7033ee2f061b20da39fc6f23b851","tid":1215962,"uid":123985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"中國駐英國大使劉曉明表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中央從未指示香港修訂《逃犯條例》</span></strong>，又認為昨日的示威由和平變成惡劣，警方需要自衛及維持秩序，不應受責備。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明接受英國廣播公司訪問，指出修例是香港政府因應台灣殺人案發起，目的是為完善法律，堵塞現行法律體系的漏洞。他說香港人走上街頭是錯誤，修例事件被歪曲，香港內部和外部的一些勢力藉事件挑起事端。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否建議香港政府放棄修例，劉曉明反問為何要這樣做。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462632-20190613.htm?fbclid=IwAR1GTpvYcFUVW57maZgiJUjf_vdC6BfBEwM0j3wmOZcLcp7iilvUQvkNud8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462632-20190613.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1GTpvYcFUVW57maZgiJUjf_vdC6BfBEwM0j3wmOZcLcp7iilvUQvkNud8&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=fce5ec78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462632-20190613.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1GTpvYcFUVW57maZgiJUjf_vdC6BfBEwM0j3wmOZcLcp7iilvUQvkNud8&h=00a4664d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462632-20190613.htm?fbclid=IwAR1GTpvYcFUVW57maZgiJUjf_vdC6BfBEwM0j3wmOZcLcp7iilvUQvkNud8</a><br />\n<br />\n棄卒??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}